        "body": "# docs: add comparison with Prism.js and Highlight.js\r\n\r\n## Description\r\n\r\nAdded a new documentation page [docs/guide/comparison.md](cci:7://file:///Users/sidduhamigi/Desktop/shiki/docs/guide/comparison.md:0:0-0:0) that compares Shiki with other popular syntax highlighters like Prism.js and Highlight.js. This addresses a common question for new users regarding accuracy, performance, and ecosystem differences.\r\n\r\nUpdated [docs/.vitepress/config.ts](cci:7://file:///Users/sidduhamigi/Desktop/shiki/docs/.vitepress/config.ts:0:0-0:0) to include the new \"Comparison\" page in the sidebar under the \"Guide\" section.\r\n\r\n## Related Issue\r\n\r\nCloses #599\r\n\r\n## Checklist\r\n\r\n- [x] Added [docs/guide/comparison.md](cci:7://file:///Users/sidduhamigi/Desktop/shiki/docs/guide/comparison.md:0:0-0:0)\r\n- [x] Updated `docs/.vitepress/config.ts`\r\n- [x] Verified content and links",
